dcterms:description: Synthetic datasets generated to emulate realistic causal structures and dependencies, sampled using the Erdős-Rényi model and following the standard structural vector autoregressive model.
dcterms:title: Synthetic Datasets

dcterms:description: Monitoring data from a cooling system of a specific room at Alibaba data center, covering the period from January 1st, 2023, to May 1st, 2023, including 38 variables (18 cold aisle temperatures and 20 air conditioning supply temperatures).
dcterms:title: Real-world Data Center Dataset
